message.body: Hey Nate. I left a check for you for the Biggie sit with Daniel. I wasn't sure when I'd see you. Hope you're having a good week:-)
Great thanks! Do u need the key back
No, just keep it for now.

Hey. Sorry for the short text msg last night. I had just left work and was super pooped. I meant to ask how the Biggie sit went for you. Hope it was ok. He's sweet but has a ton of energy! Let's connect soon:-)
He was great, no problems at all.
Oh, good. I'll keep you in mind if another Biggie sit comes up.
